      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RACCOON RIVER (1) collided in the run but raced on speed and boxed on well, finishing a one length second (22.32) in a Grade 5/6 at Cannington. Key player on best form. SERGEANT POPE (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when third (17.47) at this track. Leading chance. LANSLEY WHISPER (7) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 2 lengths (17.30) behind Double Grip at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Well placed and gets her chance. ITA KEEPING (8) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
